@@ -0,0 +1,140 @@
+# Slider Component
+
+A slider component using Swiper library for Drupal themes.
+
+## Usage
+
+### Basic Usage
+
+```twig
+{% set items = [
+  {
+    content: '<img src="path/to/image1.jpg" alt="Slide 1">'
+  },
+  {
+    content: '<img src="path/to/image2.jpg" alt="Slide 2">'
+  },
+  {
+    content: '<img src="path/to/image3.jpg" alt="Slide 3">'
+  }
+] %}
+
+{{ include('childtheme:slider', {
+  items: items
+}) }}
+```
+
+### With Custom Configuration
+
+```twig
+{% set items = [
+  {
+    content: '<img src="path/to/image1.jpg" alt="Slide 1">'
+  },
+  {
+    content: '<img src="path/to/image2.jpg" alt="Slide 2">'
+  },
+  {
+    content: '<img src="path/to/image3.jpg" alt="Slide 3">'
+  }
+] %}
+
+{{ include('childtheme:slider', {
+  items: items,
+  loop: true,
+  autoplay: true,
+  delay: 5000,
+  speed: 1000,
+  navigation: true,
+  pagination: true,
+  scrollbar: false,
+  itemsDesktop: 3,
+  itemsTablet: 2,
+  itemsMobile: 1
+}) }}
+```
+
+## Configuration Options
+
+| Option | Type | Default | Description |
+|--------|------|---------|-------------|
+| items | array | required | Array of items to display in the slider |
+| loop | boolean | false | Enable continuous loop mode |
+| speed | integer | 1500 | Duration of transition between slides (in ms) |
+| autoplay | boolean | false | Enable autoplay |
+| breakpointMobile | integer | 1 | Breakpoint for mobile devices |
+| itemsMobile | integer | 1 | Number of slides per view on mobile |
+| breakpointTablet | integer | 768 | Breakpoint for tablet devices |
+| itemsTablet | integer | 2 | Number of slides per view on tablet |
+| breakpointDesktop | integer | 1200 | Breakpoint for desktop devices |
+| itemsDesktop | integer | 3 | Number of slides per view on desktop |
+| navigation | boolean | true | Show navigation buttons |
+| delay | integer | 3000 | Delay between transitions in autoplay mode (in ms) |
+| pauseOnMouseEnter | boolean | true | Pause autoplay on mouse enter |
+| allowTouchMove | boolean | false | Allow touch move |
+| spaceBetween | integer | 24 | Space between slides |
+| pagination | boolean | true | Show pagination |
+| scrollbar | boolean | true | Show scrollbar |
+| clickablePagination | boolean | true | Make pagination clickable |
+| paginationType | string | bullets | Type of pagination (bullets, fraction, progressbar) |
+| spaceBetweenMobile | integer | 24 | Space between slides on mobile |
+| spaceBetweenTablet | integer | 24 | Space between slides on tablet |
+| spaceBetweenDesktop | integer | 24 | Space between slides on desktop |
+| effect | string | null | Transition effect (null, fade, slide, cube, coverflow, flip) |
+
+## Example with Views Integration
+
+To use this slider with Views, you can create a Views template that uses the slider component:
+
+1. Create a Views display with the content you want to show in the slider
+2. Create a Views template for your display (e.g., `views-view--your-view--your-display.html.twig`)
+3. Use the slider component in your template:
+
+```twig
+{# views-view--your-view--your-display.html.twig #}
+{% set slider_items = [] %}
+
+{% for row in rows %}
+  {% set slider_items = slider_items|merge([{
+    content: row.content
+  }]) %}
+{% endfor %}
+
+{{ include('childtheme:slider', {
+  items: slider_items,
+  loop: true,
+  autoplay: true,
+  navigation: true,
+  pagination: true
+}) }}
+```
+
+## Example with Paragraphs Integration
+
+To use this slider with Paragraphs, you can create a paragraph type for slides and then use the slider component in your paragraph template:
+
+1. Create a paragraph type for slides with fields for your slide content
+2. Create a paragraph type for the slider that references the slide paragraphs
+3. Create a template for your slider paragraph (e.g., `paragraph--slider.html.twig`)
+4. Use the slider component in your template:
+
+```twig
+{# paragraph--slider.html.twig #}
+{% set slider_items = [] %}
+
+{% for item in content.field_slides %}
+  {% if item['#paragraph'] is defined %}
+    {% set slider_items = slider_items|merge([{
+      content: item
+    }]) %}
+  {% endif %}
+{% endfor %}
+
+{{ include('childtheme:slider', {
+  items: slider_items,
+  loop: paragraph.field_loop.value,
+  autoplay: paragraph.field_autoplay.value,
+  navigation: paragraph.field_navigation.value,
+  pagination: paragraph.field_pagination.value
+}) }}
+```
